title: Heath Cummings on best Week 4 Fantasy Football, DFS plays (Football 09/27)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings to break down the Vikings-Rams game and take a look at the upcoming week in terms of the fantasy football slate. Who are some good stacks to look at? What sleepers are out there? How would Heath handle the Le'Veon Bell situation in terms of trying to trade the running back? Who are some buy low guys and guys who might have been dropped in waivers this week? All those questions answered plus much more.
